    "name": "Scholar (Sage)",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "A sage is an academic of the first order. Both a polyglot and polymath, a sage can be consulted to answer any number of questions by anyone wealthy enough to afford her considerable fees. A sage is often accompanied by a merchant prince who procures all the research materials she desires (CR 12), and together they may sit on the small council of a queen (CR 13) or king (CR 15)."
        }
